Text: 'The tremendous Trip to Himachal Pradesh for 18 days non stop exploring, trekking,
  great fellings with no money to spend on anything but the place have many secrets,
  which is difficult to know. I get to know by such situations. Places i explored..

  Malana

  Magic valley

  Bhrigu Lake

  Solang valley

  Anjani Mahadev

  Bijli Mahadev

  Hidimba temple

  Old manali

  Kasol

  Challal

  Tosh

  Manikaran

  Kullu

  Mall road manali.

  This places have great atmosphere, altitude,local eateries, crazy minded people
  and localities with positive mind and attitude. Clean and healthy Air and oxygen.

  Much things available to relax mind, reduce pain, enjoyable nights,'
